            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". The one thing about such extreme performance vehicles is that while they’re a blast to drive, they’re not a great choice for taking out on the open road. In the included video, Shmee recounts his experience ",
